Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.37,0:24:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集是暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.29,0:24:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是○
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.34,0:24:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是×
